<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Algoma Student Portal<\/strong> allows formal and prospective students in the College to create an account or log in to perform certain academic actions at ease including Course Registration, Fees Payment, Exam Results, Admission Online Application, Track Application Status, Acceptance Fees Payment, Transcript, Timetable, Academic Calander, Extra Credit Hours, Deferment of Admission and so much more.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"algoma-student-portal-how-to-login-to-algoma-student-portal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Algoma_Student_Portal_How_to_login_to_Algoma_student_portal\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc85734676\"><\/a><strong>Algoma Student Portal| How to login to Algoma student portal<br \/>\n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Student Login portal of the University is accessible as follows;<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"algoma-student-portal-algoma-now\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Algoma_Student_Portal_Algoma_Now\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc85734677\"><\/a><strong>Algoma Student Portal | Algoma Now<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>To view the portal, you will need your University Student Login ID and Password respective.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Go to the Algoma Login Page at <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/algomau.ca\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/algomau.ca<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Log in with your Login ID and Password,<\/li>\n<li>Click on the Submit or Login button.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>You should be redirected to your official portal where you can access all the information you need.<\/p>\n<p>If you have any questions or corrections regarding this post, Please, kindly Drop a Comment below and we will respond to it ASAP.<\/p>\n<p><strong>I HOPE THIS POST WAS USEFUL, PLEASE DO NOT HESITATE TO SHARE IT WITH FRIENDS!<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Algoma University Student Portal \u2013\u00a0 | How to login to Algom